{"data":[{"id":564196130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3573f9226db238f785ef3a8a395da557","url_token":"yufang-4","name":"未来捡史","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f9ed0ee9d67e00a65af36d5cad8cfcba_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f9ed0ee9d67e00a65af36d5cad8cfcba_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3573f9226db238f785ef3a8a395da557","user_type":"people","headline":"脑袋空不要紧，关键是不要进水","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564196130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546340671,"updated_time":1546356133,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e首先，不管怎么说，我很佩服他。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我自以为是个很敢想的人\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记得是小学时候吧，记得在学圆周率π，老师告诉我们无法用一个分数表示π。我却不服。我告诉老师，如果量出一个圆形物体的周长，量出直径，作比，不就能得到π的分数形式吗？老师跟我解释了半天，我也忘了怎么解释的了，只是记得老师没有说服我，但老师最后还是鼓励了我，说我是个可塑之才。（具体怎么说的忘了）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在看来这当然很荒谬，但这不正是不屈服于权威的表现吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥白尼不屈服于权威，才有了日心说。牛顿不屈服于权威，才有三定律。爱因斯坦不屈服于权威，才有相对论。普朗克没有被连续学说桎梏，才有了量子力学。可以说，不屈服于权威的精神就是创新的精神。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e更令我佩服的是，这位同学没有停留在想想的阶段，而是勇敢地做出了自己的想法。并且成功地上了知乎热搜。以这样的年龄，难道不值得我辈敬佩吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也希望当他看到哪些否认他，说他不脚踏实地的话语时不要灰心丧气，他们也许懂的比你多，但如果你坚持下来，他们以后都没你厉害。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很欣慰地看到在应试教育盛行的今天还有这样有想法的人存在，希望以后会越来越多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e更新一波——————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管怎么说，比我强了已经，有没有“知乎大神”强就不知道了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e吸引流量，那是必要的，毕竟孩子嘛，希望获得关注。我高中也喜欢上课插嘴呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只不过他没有意识到我们这个社会里的杠精有多么多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望大家对一个孩子宽容点吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e宽松的环境更容易培养出有创造力的人才。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果有人对杠精这个名词对号入座，那我先道个歉。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"首先，不管怎么说，我很佩服他。我自以为是个很敢想的人记得是小学时候吧，记得在学圆周率π，老师告诉我们无法用一个分数表示π。我却不服。我告诉老师，如果量出一个圆形物体的周长，量出直径，作比，不就能得到π的分数形式吗？老师跟我解释了半天，我也…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=433\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Cs